{
  "stem": "3341.3",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A weaving stool, it's quite a big machine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I collected so many machines and in the end, the schoolyard was full.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they came in pieces.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so our first work was, me and my friend, to bring the machine, to put them, to assemble them together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's how it started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were there up to the time when there was an uprising that I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In middle of '44, a whole area, which was not very far from this Ruzomberok, where was this school, that was also in a mountainous area.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Three divisions of Slovakian army, which is about 60,000 to 90,000 soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So for that area, quite a big number of soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Three divisions.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They started to be-- they started the militaristic uprising against the mighty German army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was towards the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every intelligent German and intelligent Slovak knew that Germany is losing the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then, when they went from-- no, the big town, which the Russians took over-- Stalingrad and all the other towns, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the German army was retreating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so the courage of the Slovakian-- because in the Slovakian army, the officers were not fascistically-- not all, but maybe half were not fascistically-minded.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Slovakian country, as small as it was, about one third of the population was Protestant and two thirds were Catholic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Catholics were the more followers of the fascist Slovakian movement because the first president of Slovakia-- I forgot to mention-- was a Catholic priest.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was hanged after the war as a war criminal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We take a break.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
